{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/judg7ads","slide":8,"name":"内容占位符 2","text":"Tofino 可编程交换机\nTNA(Tofino Native Architecture)是以 P416 为基础的体系结构，提供了映射到 Tofino 交换机的 P4 编程接口\n\n","bbox":[96.55181102362205,201.63968503937008,1775.7175853018373,850.3603149606299]}
{"kind":"image","id":"im/83itgfml","slide":8,"name":"图片 183","text":"","bbox":[172.5471916010499,380.95380577427824,1574.9056167979004,642.4945931758531]}
